    <briefdescription>
<para>Boot manager — reset reason, boot counter, safe-mode detection. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Uses the parameter store to persist boot state across resets. Detects crash loops (too many resets without a successful &quot;mark healthy&quot;) and can trigger safe-mode behavior.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structSYN__Boot" kindref="compound">SYN_Boot</ref><sp/>boot;</highlight></codeline>
